  "body": "**Description**\r\n\r\nWhen user recovers a BIP39 12 words mnemonic, and the mnemonic does not fullfill BIP 39:\r\n- one or some words are not part of the dictionary we store in status\r\n- the checksum is not good\r\n\r\nthen we show a basic error message following step 1 of the description in\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/9050 \r\n\r\n**Problem**\r\n\r\nSome guidance could be provided to the user for better UX \r\n- to avoid typing wrong words \r\n- to understand what is incorrect when the mnemonic is incorrect \r\n\r\n**Solution**\r\n\r\nneeds design work is needed to provide the right user experience for this \r\nneeds implementation",
